dct_title_s: Fairview, Cliffside Park and Ridgefield, Bergen County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Includes text. Sheets 21, 30-42, 52-54 of Palisades, N.J. series. Sheets 30-32 show Fairview and part of Cliffside Park, sheets 33-42 show Cliffside Park, sheets 52-54 show Fort Lee and part of Cliffside Park.
